room_title: Escape room "Beasley's Billions" by Tick Tock Escape Room in Overland Park
room_description: You’ve been invited to the home of your billionaire-uncle, Thurston Beasley III, for the reading of his will. When you arrive, you meet other family members you didn’t even know existed! Beasley has directed you to be locked in his den for an hour and has prepared a series of puzzles and tasks to see if his family can work together as a team. Will you be able to escape and win Beasley’s Billions in time?
